Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.82,Episode Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,271)\fade(255,0,255,0,800,3450,4800)}Episode 20
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.82,Episode Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349,414)\fade(255,0,255,0,800,3450,4800)}Sūn Cè's death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.61,0:00:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sūn Cè dominated Jiāngdōng, seizing Lújiāng, gaining momentum to his cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.25,0:00:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Once finished, Zhāng Hóng was sent to{\i1} Xǔchāng {\i0}to announce their victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But his request to become Grand Marshal Cáo Cāo and so it was refused
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.79,0:00:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sūn Cè become concerned for this,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.20,0:00:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and began planning a counterattack to Xǔchāng.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.85,0:00:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, the Administrator of Wú Commandery,\N{\i1}Xǔ Gòng{\i0}, contacted Xǔchāng in secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:44.26,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(83,325)\fade(255,0,255,0,460,1620,2220)}Xǔ Gòng
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.35,0:00:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,informing Cáo Cāo of the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.02,0:00:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Go by the river,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.75,0:01:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,deliver this to the Chancellor Cáo.\NMake sure no one else sees this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.56,0:01:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.89,0:01:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is extremely classified. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.87,0:01:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.09,0:01:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Halt! Who is crossing the river?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.34,0:01:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Administrator of Wú Commandery, {\i0}Xǔ Gòng!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.37,0:01:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We are returning back to \Nthe offices after Sūn Cè army drills!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire, our army is now prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.44,0:01:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can suppress \NHuáng Zǔ and cut down Liú Biǎo,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.30,0:01:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,we can rely on the Yangtze River as our bulwark for Jiāngdōng, and bring peace to our land.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.70,0:01:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Zǐbù, the land you speak of is different from mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.71,0:02:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, Cáo Cāo commands all in the Emperor's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.55,0:02:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuán Shào has the{\i1} Héběi {\i0}region,\N a tiger among men.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.55,0:02:06.44,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: Héběi is one of the names for Jì-Province,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How could I be satisfied with only the Jiāngdōng region?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire has overseen vigorous\N training for our men yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and now we are here to oversee the building of our ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.44,0:02:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it possible... is it possible that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Report! An envoy of Xǔ Gòng was crossing the river, and was detained by our patrols!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.15,0:02:46.48,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}"Sūn Cè is valiant and indomitable, akin to Xiàng Jí.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.15,0:02:50.28,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: Xiàng Jí, styled Xiàng Yǔ, was the Hegemon-King of Chǔ, \Na fierce warlord who advanced the fall of Qín dynasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.86,0:02:50.30,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}The court ought to reward him, then summon him back to the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.42,0:02:52.68,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}You must not let him dominate Jiāngdōng..."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.68,0:02:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}...'Or he will become a menace'.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.64,0:03:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The realm is in anarchy, the lords scramble for power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.54,0:03:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Those without ambition, can only serve others.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Zǐbù, now you understand the land that I dream of...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:33.34,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(104,342)\fade(255,0,255,0,500,1700,2180)}Sūn Cè\NStyled: Bófú
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,General Sūn Cè has sent a message!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.16,0:04:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,General Sūn is hosting a banquet for the envoys of Jīng-Province.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.84,0:04:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and has asked for you, sir, to come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me prepare my chariot, I'll come after.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.14,0:04:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no need, Mr. Xǔ! \NGeneral Sūn has prepared one, just for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.38,0:04:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.50,0:04:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.27,0:05:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.02,0:05:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.20,0:05:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire, that is-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.37,0:05:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That is an {\i1}Immortal!{\i0} A god among men!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.89,0:05:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Scram! Scram!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What {\i1}Immortal!?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ask who he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.02,0:05:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, the exalted Immortal will punish us if we don't kneel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.48,0:05:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire! Get down now! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Zǐbù, don't tell me you believe in this nonsense too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.15,0:05:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.05,0:06:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire! If you don't kneel, \Nthen you better get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.26,0:06:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't stay here, sire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I am {\i1}Sūn Cè of Jiāngdōng!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They should be kneeling to {\i1}me!{\i0} Damn peons!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Zhòngmóu{\i0}, task General Chéng Pǔ \Nto locate those three shady men.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Those men are of no importance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell General Chéng to capture that foul sorcerer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:06:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.11,0:07:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire, peasants praying for that\N Immortal is only a trifle matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.24,0:07:05.78,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,650,2040,2520)\pos(619.911,336.356)}Zhāng Zhāo\NStyled: Zǐbù
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need for anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.12,0:07:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I not be angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.10,0:07:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the lord of this region!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I prostrate myself to some heretic magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I will find out who that revolting sorcerer is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.22,0:07:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop his bewitching of the citizens of this city!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.64,0:07:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Your son pays his respects to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.49,0:07:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My son, what is troubling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, why have you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been inside too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.64,0:07:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard recently there's an Immortal in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They say he can work miracles, curing the sick, and seeing the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing else to do, \Nso I want to see him for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, the markets are messy, why go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, there are no such thing as Immortals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I seldom go out to a walk, \NI just want to expel the boredom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Rumors may not always be false.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.95,0:08:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The world can hold many surprises unimaginable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out! All of you, come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Who is it? Who told of that \Nheretic street magician to my mother!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire, we can take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to upset your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.16,0:09:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you still kneeling for? Help our lord to rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,With that foul sorcerer here, I will not rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.12,0:09:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I rest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.75,0:09:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I am going hunting in Dāntú Mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.22,0:09:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No more of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:19.04,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Back then, on the Shéntíng Ridge,\N I ascended to the temple there,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.48,0:10:23.60,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}there I swore an oath, \Nfacing the idols of our illustrious heroes,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:27.64,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}If I can revive my late father's foundations in Jiāngdōng,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.78,0:10:32.30,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}I would rebuild that temple, \Nvenerate it at every snake's hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:32.96,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: 9-11 A.M. based on {\i1}the Earthly Branches.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.14,0:10:37.70,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Today, Jiāngdōng is in prosperity. \NIt is time to honor that oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:42.16,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}If at this mountain peak I could build another temple,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:46.04,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}one which can let the people\N stand tall and see the distance,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:50.56,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}and revere our pioneers, wouldn't that be better?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.28,0:12:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.41,0:12:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.24,0:13:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.02,0:13:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.02,0:13:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.42,0:13:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire? Sire?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire! Sire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.26,0:13:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire! Sire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.00,0:13:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I was too careless!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.95,0:13:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I was too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.45,0:13:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Zǐbù,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to build a temple for {\i1}Guāngwǔ{\i0}, so that the people can see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:47.70,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: Emperor Guāngwǔ Liú Xiù was an imperial scion who lived as a farmer, but would later restore the Han Dynasty in 25 AD
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,... So that people never forget... \NThe greatness men can achieve...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.56,0:13:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.17,0:13:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How severe is his condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The arrow was poisoned.\NI'm afraid it has already entered his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.35,0:14:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He must rest for a hundred days and do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My son has suffered this disaster, \Nall because of his volatility and arrogance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.48,0:14:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.25,0:14:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,To the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.15,0:15:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire, you can get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.48,0:15:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.74,0:15:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A blessing from the Heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.41,0:15:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.54,0:15:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What blessings from Heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.26,0:16:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I am destined to be a hero, not to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How could Xǔ Gòng's servants be able to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't strain yourself, my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,For two months, I've kept my hope for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.95,0:16:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You are still injured.\NYou must go back and rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.48,0:16:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You were in peril, so your mother and I, and all the servants,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.70,0:16:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,prayed on your behalf to\N the Immortal deities for a swift recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.46,0:16:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}O spirits, please forgive him, \Nmy son is young and passionate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let all disaster befall on to me in his stead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This whole mansion has fallen into devil worship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:17:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I, Sūn Cè, be aided by some {\i1}mystical deities?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I detest witchcraft, and those \Nheretic prophets who mislead men's hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.90,0:17:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Take them off! Don't let me see them again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.86,0:17:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Who dares!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.42,0:17:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Without the Immortals' help,\Nwould you be here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sūn Cè's wound had started to recover slightly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.52,0:17:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Zhāng Hóng, who went to Xǔchāng to report Sūn Cè's victories,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}had an envoy return in his stead, now a visitor to the mansion.{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.75,0:18:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, how many days have you been here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(125,365)\fade(255,0,255,0,460,1860,2260)}The Envoy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been six days.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,When will you return to Xǔchāng?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.82,0:18:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I will go back to Xǔchāng tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.62,0:18:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,General, can you inform Zhāng Hóng of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.67,0:18:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I would, only that Zǐbù won't let me speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire, your wound hasn't healed yet \Nand you've been playing weiqi for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.37,0:18:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that's enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.04,0:18:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.58,0:18:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the envoy will return to Xǔchāng tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I will only ask one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please allow me this one, Zǐbù.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.10,0:18:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to ask this gentleman
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.58,0:19:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Does Cáo Cāo really fear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.40,0:19:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.82,0:19:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Cáo Cāo does fear Your Lordship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,His advisors too all respect your Lordship. Only...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Only what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Only what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.60,0:19:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,His Lordship said, he only asks one question.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.39,0:19:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes yes yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I have spoken too much, I must take my leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me one last sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.94,0:19:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope my Lord will get well soon with vim and vigor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.48,0:19:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What vim and vigor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.82,0:19:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean to anger me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.24,0:19:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.33,0:19:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would disregard me, {\i1}Sūn Cè?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.90,0:20:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Only Guō Jiā disregards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.07,0:20:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Guō Jiā?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.55,0:20:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, please,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't repeat Guō Jiā's words!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I take my leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Halt, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.10,0:20:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, you've already started, \Nwhy not finish your words before leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.07,0:20:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you make our lord angrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.44,0:20:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what the words are, please finish before leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.88,0:20:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Guō Jiā had told Lord Cáo,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,that there's nothing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.89,0:21:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that Your Lordship is a bloated \Nand arrogant cretin. A barbaric imbecile.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.59,0:21:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What more?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.42,0:21:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.08,0:21:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.44,0:21:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He said... Your Lordship will die like a lout!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.44,0:21:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire, Guō Jiā is just a base-born. He deserves death.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.43,0:21:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire, please calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.14,0:21:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The nerve of that cur!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.67,0:22:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I will crush Xǔchāng!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.62,0:22:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Zǐbù.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.35,0:22:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been many days since\NYuán Shào sent his envoy, Chén Zhèn.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.54,0:22:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you report?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.35,0:22:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.23,0:22:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You. Inform master Chén Zhèn...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.77,0:22:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I will ally with Yuán Shào against Cáo Cāo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.67,0:22:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.61,0:22:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, summon our generals to the city top.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.18,0:22:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And tell mister Chén Zhèn to come as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.35,0:22:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We will discuss our strike against Cáo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctor warned sire to rest for a hundred days.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.46,0:22:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you sacrifice your well-being like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.57,0:23:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen, do rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.55,0:23:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Chén Zhèn is Yuán Shào's envoy and shall be the guest of honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.16,0:23:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.84,0:24:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.58,0:24:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Every gentlemen present, \Nwhether be the veteran ministers,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.79,0:24:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,or all the fierce generals who founded\NJiāngdōng and followed me in conquests,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.26,0:24:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,or like Zǐyì.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.60,0:24:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All great champions, heroes of the battlefield,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.13,0:24:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,for me to have Jiāngdōng as part of my legacy,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.00,0:24:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it is thanks to all of you, that we could be here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.97,0:24:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Please accept all my gratitude, my noble men!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.92,0:24:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,May Your Lordship recover and lead Jiāngdōng to greatness!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.46,0:25:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, the men of Jiāngdōng are fed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.12,0:25:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The commoners live in peace and prosper.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.30,0:25:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,These developments are indeed gratifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.93,0:25:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.82,0:25:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,To protect Jiāngdōng, \None has to hold great ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.66,0:25:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Those without ambitions will only be subject to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.41,0:25:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We can join with Yuán Shào and resist Cáo Cāo.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.05,0:25:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is now our goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.45,0:25:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If we want peace, we must prepare for war.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.76,0:25:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Build a great navy and fortify our position.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.33,0:25:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,then we can march north and besiege Xǔchāng.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.41,0:25:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why look out?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.98,0:25:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Immortal Yú is passing by down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.44,0:25:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We generals wish to pay our respects.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.80,0:26:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that heretic again! Throw him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.76,0:26:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.96,0:26:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Superstitious hogwash!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.90,0:26:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,For even officers to be fooled by these lies,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.64,0:27:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,if this continues, how can I conquer the realm?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.12,0:26:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.34,0:27:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.95,0:27:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.46,0:27:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Sire, he is called Yú Jí.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.46,0:27:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}He travels everywhere to administer medicines.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.98,0:27:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}He has healed many, no disease has ever stumped him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.85,0:27:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}They call him an Immortal.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.48,0:27:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Sire, this isn't to be taken lightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.89,0:27:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Scram!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.07,0:27:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Get that foul sorcerer and off with his head!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.07,0:27:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone against me, shall follow with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.14,0:27:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire, you can't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.05,0:27:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.32,0:27:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.40,0:27:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Yú has never done anything wrong in all his years in Jiāngdōng.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.98,0:27:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire, you mustn't kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.00,0:27:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorcerer swines must be slaughtered.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.10,0:27:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,General, can't you see the people below revere Yú Jí?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.40,0:27:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.78,0:27:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Please sir, this isn't the time or place.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.44,0:27:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You are all men of reason, \Nwhy be unreasonable now?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.77,0:28:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I must vanquish this evil at all costs, for the good of men!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.81,0:28:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,General, please spare him, for our sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.11,0:28:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You wish to rebel, {\i1}for Yú Jí?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.99,0:28:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare bewitch the people?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.16,0:28:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I only speak on behalf of heaven to save people.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.24,0:29:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I would never take anything from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.57,0:29:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How could that be bewitching them?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.82,0:29:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you take nothing, then where did you get your clothes? What do you eat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.11,0:29:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play coy!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.65,0:29:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If I let you go, all will fall into chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.52,0:29:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Son, cease this!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.29,0:29:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Son, you know killing Immortals without reason bears ill!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.07,0:29:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What? How could you not trust me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.34,0:29:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, you know who I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.41,0:29:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The empire is still in turmoil. My task is not over!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.04,0:29:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This sorcerer brings disaster, lulling\N the officials and generals into subservience
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.78,0:29:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,People bend their knees to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.69,0:29:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, how will I realize my father's dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.83,0:30:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I not know?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.00,0:30:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet because you disrespected \Nthe deities did you invoke calamity.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.17,0:30:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I- I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.38,0:30:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The assassins of the mountain\Nwere Xǔ Gòng's retainers.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.25,0:30:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I was careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.04,0:30:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But how could you be so foolish, \Nbringing trouble to your own son!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.42,0:30:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.26,0:30:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My son...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.49,0:30:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father was also short-tempered and rash.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.20,0:30:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He did not heed others, \Nand died in those mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.74,0:30:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you not understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.76,0:31:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are an 'Immortal', why kneel?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.61,0:33:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.05,0:33:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you speaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.95,0:33:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.82,0:33:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to tell the Grand Lady and Mrs.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.46,0:33:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not my place to speak on such matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.27,0:33:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.81,0:33:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.22,0:33:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I  wouldn't dare lie, but our Lord... he is dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.69,0:33:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,His Lordship's venom within hasn't healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.92,0:34:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And because of his outburst, \Nthe poison has spread to his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.53,0:34:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It infected his heart and lungs.\NThis ailment is already too late to heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.57,0:34:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This lowly servant has been well treated by his Lordship.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.14,0:34:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I regret my inability to heal him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.10,0:34:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.91,0:34:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it is over...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.21,0:34:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, summon my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.79,0:34:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Zhòngmóu...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.02,0:35:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Zhòngmóu...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.50,0:35:27.14,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,350,2140,2320)\pos(590.578,309.956)}Sūn Quán\NStyled: Zhòngmóu
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.30,0:35:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Zhòngmóu...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.92,0:35:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}The realm is in chaos. But with men of Wúyuè,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.92,0:35:49.62,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: Wúyuè is one of the historical names of the Jiāngnán/Jiāngdōng region
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.74,0:35:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}and the strength of Three Rivers, you will have a future.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.92,0:36:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Zǐbù.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.38,0:36:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.99,0:36:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.44,0:36:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}In gathering the men of Jiāngdōng, in leading legions through fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.94,0:36:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}in challenging the world, \Nmy brother does not compare to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.72,0:36:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Yet in recognizing talent, \Nin sacrificing one's own being to defend Jiāngdōng,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.58,0:36:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}I do not compare to my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.42,0:37:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}My brother, the hardship father \Nand I went through to achieve all this...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.18,0:37:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}You must understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.76,0:37:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.16,0:37:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is not the time to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.97,0:37:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It is up to you now to uphold our family's legacy!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.07,0:37:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.20,0:37:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.80,0:38:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Mother, I know my years from Heaven are over
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.86,0:38:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}and I can no longer serve you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.94,0:38:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.429,436.857)}Now I shall entrust my cause to my younger brother,
